Company Description:
Private Capital Advisors is a boutique investment banking firm that focuses on private placements and mergers and acquisitions advisory services.

Private Capital Advisors provides a spectrum of services including:

• sourcing and negotiating investments from institutional and strategic equity firms;

• representing buyers and sellers in merger and acquisition transactions;

• building financial models designed to expedite due diligence for both clients and investors; and

• preparing professional investor presentations customized for the private capital market.

